01:03:00.690 --> 01:03:03.360 align:middle line:84%
But if you do induction
for each subtree,

01:03:03.360 --> 01:03:06.890 align:middle line:84%
you can only guarantee that
the degree inside each subtree

01:03:06.890 --> 01:03:07.680 align:middle line:90%
