01:03:40.040 --> 01:03:41.550 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

01:03:41.550 --> 01:03:42.690 align:middle line:84%
PABLO SHMERKIN: Yeah,
what is confusing you,

01:03:42.690 --> 01:03:43.970 align:middle line:84%
you're thinking about
